        <dc:creator><![CDATA[agiletortoise]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>As <a class="mention" href="https://forums.getdrafts.com/u/sylumer">@sylumer</a> mentions, it can be done with scripting to allow a great amount of control, but if you are looking for the most straight forward way, start with the <a href="https://actions.getdrafts.com/a/1Ia">Event</a> action - which ships in the default “Basic” action group or can be installed from the link above.</p>
<p>There are a number of other ready to use actions to work with calendars as well, if you search the <a href="https://actions.getdrafts.com">Action Directory</a> for “event”, “calendar” and similar terms.</p>
<p>Many also use Drafts along with Fantastical to get natural language parsing features. Details in our <a href="https://forums.getdrafts.com/t/using-fantastical-with-drafts/25">Fantastical integration guide</a>.</p>
